g.text: It is a wrapper on Scapy's Packet. We use a wrapper because we don't want to save Scapy' Packets (since the Scapy's Packet has a lot of information (which we do not use most of them), and saving them required lots of memory, so to decrease the memory usage, we save only needed information in this calss).
